        <h2>Active Listening</h2>

        <p>Active listening is a skill that can be learned and is a vital part of being a good instructor. To be a good active listener, remember to:</p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside sr-only">
          <li>Maintain eye contact</li>
          <li>Avoid interruptions</li>
          <li>Be aware of your body language messages</li>
          <li>Encourage responses from your student</li>
          <li>Summarise your understanding of what the student has said when they have finished</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

